{"name":"Lemon Chicken Orzo","slug":"lemon-chicken-orzo","description":"<p>Love lemon and chicken? This recipe is creamy and comforting. A one-pot, Mediterranean-inspired dinner the whole family will love!</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"oil","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"boneless skinless chicken thighs","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Lemon Chicken Orzo Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":"divided"},{"name":"water","quantity":"1 <sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"cherry tomatoes","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"orzo","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"capers","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":"drained"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"baby spinach","quantity":"4 cups","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Heat oil over medium-high&nbsp;heat in a <a data-item-id=\"4592bb8a-4986-4f89-8253-3ff61af8d78e\" href=\"\">Sauté Pan</a>.</li>\n  <li>Season chicken thighs with 1 tbsp of seasoning. Add chicken to preheated pan; brown 2 min per side.</li>\n  <li>Whisk remaining seasoning with hot water.</li>\n  <li>To pan, add reserved seasoning mixture, cherry tomatoes, orzo, capers, and butter. Stir to combine; bring to a boil. Reduce to simmer and cover; cook 12 min or until orzo is tender.</li>\n  <li>Increase heat and gradually stir in spinach until wilted and sauce thickens.</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"onion_free","name":"Onion-free"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"chicken___poultry","name":"Chicken & Poultry"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"garlic_free","name":"Garlic-free"},{"slug":"stovetop_978bc23","name":"Stovetop"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":340,"fat":15,"saturatedFat":4.5,"transFat":0.2,"cholesterol":85,"sodium":470,"carbohydrate":23,"fiber":4,"sugars":4,"protein":26},"tips":"<p>This dish will be very saucy right off the stove—the sauce will thicken as it sits.</p>","perfectlyBalanceYourPlate":"<p>Serve with 1 small wholegrain bun.</p>"}